name: TeaCrypto Finance
description: TeaCrypto Finance is a multi-chain financial application born with the aim of bringing an open currency solution to investors, built to integrate inter-chain solutions in savings. payment, transactions, money market, ... DeFi TCF ecosystem develops a variety of products to serve users wishing to easily access DeFi, including: TCF Dashboard, TCF Exchange , TCF Lend, TCF Portfolio, Yield Farming, TCF NFT, TCF Pay.
